### Send GET request to get all users
GET localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

### Send POST request with json body to create user
POST localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "KateHori",
  "password": "teste",
  "type": 0
}

### Send GET request to get user by id
GET localhost:8080/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Send PUT request to update a user with json body by id
PUT localhost:8080/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "teste123"
}

### Send POST request with json body to login user
POST localhost:8080/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "KateHori",
  "password": "teste123"
}

### Send DELETE request to delete a user by id
DELETE localhost:8080/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

